	<p>
		<lb n="1"/>kōraikōṭṭu-p poruṇaṉ ṅāka<unclear>ṅkatturai</unclear>
		<lb n="2"/>ciṭu-p poṉ-mut-u
		<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṭ-puḷḷi <unclear>poṉ</unclear>
		<lb n="4" break="no"/>-mut-uṭ-k-kāṭṭi pūca
		<lb n="5" break="no"/>l-uṭ
		<lb n="6"/>paṭṭa
		<lb n="7"/>kal
	</p>
	
