<div type="translation" resp="part:emfr">
      		
	<p n="1-4">
		<supplied reason="subaudible">This is the</supplied> stone <supplied reason="subaudible">erected when</supplied>
		Poṉ Mutuṭpuḷḷi<note>Poṉ, literally "gold," is an honourific prefix, that could be translated as "excellent."</note>
		<supplied reason="explanation">and</supplied>
		<unclear>Poṉ</unclear> Mutuṭkkāṭṭi
		died in a fight <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>pūcal-uḷ</foreign></supplied>
		...
		in Kōraikōṭu.		
	</p>
	
</div>
      	
